images:
[
  {
    "caption": "Discover your signature scent without the luxury price tag.",
    "prompt": "A sleek, minimalist perfume bottle centered on a clean, light gray background. Soft, diffused lighting creates gentle reflections on the bottle's surface. The bottle is elegantly styled, perhaps with a simple gold cap and subtle label. The caption text is cleanly overlaid in a modern sans-serif font, white with a soft shadow for readability. Focus on the bottle's form and the sense of refined simplicity."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Explore diverse options under 1000 INR.",
    "prompt": "A dynamic arrangement of 3-5 distinct perfume bottles from different brands, arranged diagonally across the frame. Each bottle showcases unique shapes, colors, and labels, emphasizing variety. The bottles are partially visible, with some labels clearly readable. A soft, warm ambient light highlights the bottles. The caption text is positioned at the bottom, bold and modern, contrasting with the bottles. Focus on showcasing the range and accessibility of affordable luxury."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Perfect for gifting – luxury they'll love.",
    "prompt": "A beautifully wrapped gift box prominently displayed on a soft, textured surface (e.g., velvet or linen). The box features a luxurious ribbon and a small, elegant perfume bottle peeking out from the top. Soft, inviting lighting highlights the textures. The caption text is elegantly placed near the box, perhaps on a subtle banner or tag. Focus on the presentation, the gift's appeal, and the promise of a luxurious experience."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Enjoy your favorite scent daily, affordably.",
    "prompt": "A stylish person (e.g., a woman or man) holding a perfume bottle, looking content and relaxed. They are positioned in a comfortable, well-lit interior setting (e.g., a cozy living room or a stylish bathroom). The focus is on the person's expression of enjoyment and the act of applying perfume. The bottle is visible, perhaps being held or sprayed. Soft, warm lighting enhances the scene. The caption text is integrated subtly, perhaps on a nearby surface or as a soft overlay, conveying the theme of accessible daily luxury."
  }
]

[
  {
    "caption": "Calm & Heal Melting Balm - 4.6 stars, $799",
    "prompt": "A luxurious, golden-hued melting balm in a sleek, minimalist jar. Close-up shot showing the product melting seamlessly into dry, sensitive skin on a model's forearm, revealing a radiant, hydrated complexion. Soft, natural lighting emphasizes the product's soothing texture and the skin's immediate transformation. Background is a serene, neutral-toned setting with subtle hints of calming botanicals."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Universal Vitamin C Skin Refiner - 4.5 stars, $799",
    "prompt": "A vibrant, pearlescent Vitamin C serum in a modern, minimalist bottle. Close-up of the product being gently pressed into the skin of a model's cheek, highlighting a luminous, even-toned complexion with visible radiance. Bright, natural daylight creates a fresh, energizing atmosphere. Background features soft, diffused light and subtle reflections of the product's glow."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Skin Softening Cleanser (Meaningful Beauty) - 4.3 stars, $6.99",
    "prompt": "A creamy, pale pink cleanser in a simple, elegant pump bottle. Close-up of the product being lathered between fingertips on a model's damp hand, with a focus on the gentle, non-foaming texture. The skin appears soft, supple, and balanced. Soft, warm lighting creates a calming, spa-like ambiance. Background is a clean, minimalist bathroom setting."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Dermstore Skincare Collection - 4.1+ stars, $6.99 - $799",
    "prompt": "An elegant, curated display of Dermstore's top-rated skincare products. Show a stylish vanity or shelf featuring multiple jars, bottles, and pumps (including the Balm, Refiner, and Cleanser) alongside a price range indicator. Products are arranged aesthetically with soft, warm lighting. Background is a sophisticated, neutral-toned setting emphasizing luxury and accessibility. Text overlay highlights key ratings and price points."
  }
]

[
  {
    "caption": "Diverse hands applying different skincare products, showcasing a range of textures and application methods. Caption: 'Find your perfect match from cleansing to moisturizing.'",
    "prompt": "A vibrant, diverse group of hands (different skin tones, ages, genders) applying various skincare products. Show a range of textures: a pump bottle of moisturizer being squeezed, a dropper bottle of serum being dispensed, a jar of cream being scooped, a spray bottle being misted, and a spatula scooping a balm. Hands demonstrate different application methods: one hand gently patting a serum into the skin, another smoothing a moisturizer with upward strokes, a third tapping an eye cream around the orbital bone, and a fourth using a brush to apply a mask. Soft, natural lighting. Background is a clean, minimalist white surface. Focus on the hands and products, conveying a sense of personalized skincare routine."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Close-up of a luxurious Lancme moisturizer bottle and a Sephora Collection serum bottle side-by-side. Caption: 'Luxury meets value: Lancme's prestige and Sephora's accessible excellence.'",
    "prompt": "A luxurious, high-end Lancme moisturizer bottle (gold accents, elegant design) and a sleek, modern Sephora Collection serum bottle (clean white label, minimalist design) placed side-by-side on a reflective surface. The Lancme bottle is positioned slightly higher, emphasizing its premium status. Soft, diffused lighting highlights the textures of the bottles and the reflective surface. The Lancme bottle has a gold cap and a sophisticated label, while the Sephora bottle has a simple, clean label. The scene conveys a direct comparison between luxury and accessible value. Focus on the bottles, their labels, and the reflective surface. Caption text subtly integrated as a watermark or overlay."
  },
  {
    "caption": "A sleek, modern skincare shelf displaying Dermalogica, Givenchy, and Indeed Labs products. Caption: 'Build your routine with trusted leaders: Dermalogica, Givenchy, and Indeed Labs.'",
    "prompt": "A modern, minimalist white shelf displaying an array of premium skincare products. Arrange bottles and jars from Dermalogica (professional-looking, often with green or blue accents), Givenchy (elegant, high-fashion design), and Indeed Labs (innovative, science-focused packaging) in a visually appealing, organized manner. Products include cleansers, moisturizers, serums, and eye creams. The arrangement should showcase the diversity of brands and products while emphasizing their premium nature. Soft, warm, natural lighting. Focus on the products and the clean, sophisticated shelf setup. Caption text integrated as a subtle overlay or graphic element on the shelf."
  },
  {
    "caption": "A satisfied customer smiling, holding a Sephora Collection moisturizer. Caption: 'Experience the results: High ratings, high performance, high satisfaction.'",
    "prompt": "A happy, diverse customer (smiling, relaxed expression) holding a Sephora Collection moisturizer bottle. The customer is looking directly at the camera with a confident, satisfied expression. The moisturizer bottle is prominently displayed in their hand. Soft, natural lighting. Simple, clean background (white or light neutral). The customer's skin looks healthy and radiant. Focus on the customer's face and the product in their hand. Caption text integrated as a subtle overlay or graphic element near the customer's shoulder or the product. Conveys trust, satisfaction, and the product's effectiveness."
  }
]

[
  {
    "caption": "Stunning close-up of Philosophy Amazing Grace Magnolia Eau de Parfum bottle on a luxurious surface",
    "prompt": "Ultra-close macro shot of the iconic Philosophy Amazing Grace Magnolia Eau de Parfum crystal bottle. Focus on the intricate crystal facets catching soft, diffused light. The bottle rests on a sleek, polished marble surface with subtle reflections. Soft, luxurious background bokeh. Emphasize the bottle's elegance, craftsmanship, and the allure of the fragrance within. Shot with shallow depth of field, natural lighting."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Hands applying BlushBee Organic Beauty Lip Nourishing Matte Ruby Pink gloss",
    "prompt": "Close-up shot of a woman's hands applying BlushBee Organic Beauty Lip Nourishing Matte Ruby Pink gloss. Focus on the glossy, ruby-pink gloss being smoothly glided onto the lips. The hands are soft, manicured, and appear luxurious. The gloss has a subtle shimmer and rich color payoff visible on the lips. Soft, warm, natural lighting. Background is softly blurred, suggesting a serene, intimate setting. Highlight the product's natural ingredients and the luxurious feel of application."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Professional makeup artist applying MAKE UP FOR EVER 27 Charmed blush on a model's cheek",
    "prompt": "Professional makeup artist's hand applying the MAKE UP FOR EVER 27 Charmed blush palette to a model's cheek. Focus on the artist's skilled hand blending the vibrant, professional-grade blush onto the model's skin. The model's cheek is softly lit, showcasing the flawless, buildable color payoff of the 27 shades. Background is a clean, professional makeup station with tools and products visible. Emphasize the precision, color range, and professional application technique."
  },
  {
    "caption": "FAE Beauty Glossy Cherry Red High Shine Lip Gloss bottle with a glossy finish",
    "prompt": "High-gloss, reflective shot of the FAE Beauty Glossy Cherry Red Lip Gloss bottle. The bottle's surface is highly polished, capturing intense highlights and reflections. The cherry red color is vibrant and saturated. The bottle sits on a reflective surface, amplifying the glossy effect. Soft, dramatic lighting to emphasize the sheen and luxurious texture. Focus on the bottle's design and the promise of high-shine, non-sticky wear."
  }
]

