  {
    "caption": "Perfumers Club Gift Set - Variety at its Finest",
    "prompt": "A beautifully arranged display of three elegant perfume bottles (Dreamer, EternalLove, Iconic) in a luxurious gift box, showcasing the 150ml total volume. Soft, warm lighting highlights the sleek packaging and the distinct bottle designs. A subtle background of silk scarves and a velvet cushion emphasizes the premium, discovery-focused experience. The scene conveys value, variety, and the perfect introduction to high-quality fragrances."
  },
  {
    "caption": "ENVY Blush - The Premium Mid-Range Choice",
    "prompt": "A sophisticated close-up of the ENVY Blush perfume bottle (60ml) against a minimalist, elegant backdrop. The bottle features a sleek, modern design with a soft blush-colored accent. Soft, diffused lighting emphasizes the luxurious texture and the premium feel. A single, elegantly dressed woman's hand gently touches the bottle, conveying sophistication, quality, and the allure of a high-end fragrance accessible to discerning consumers."
  },
  {
    "caption": "5th Avenue NYC Red - The Iconic Luxury Signature",
    "prompt": "A timeless, iconic perfume bottle (5th Avenue NYC Red, 100ml) centered on a polished marble surface. The bottle design exudes classic luxury with its distinctive shape and label. Soft, dramatic lighting creates a sense of heritage and prestige. The scene is minimalist and elegant, focusing solely on the bottle as a symbol of timeless sophistication and ultimate luxury, appealing to collectors and those seeking a signature scent."
  },
  {
    "caption": "Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet - Exclusivity Perfume",
    "prompt": "A rare, exclusive perfume bottle (Miss Dior Blooming Bouquet, limited edition) presented on a luxurious velvet cushion within a dimly lit, opulent setting. The bottle is the sole focus, radiating an aura of extreme rarity and high-end collectibility. Soft, dramatic lighting highlights the bottle's unique design and the sense of exclusivity. The atmosphere conveys prestige, desirability, and the allure of owning a piece of Dior's limited artistry."
  }
]
